 ;">\n<div class="accContent__inner">\n<div class="accContent__wrapper">\n<
 div id="component_4157933">\n<p>Please submit a full draft of the paper OR
  a 1000-word (minimum) abstract by <strong>19 December 2025</strong>.</p><
 h3>Abstract criteria</h3><p>If sending an abstract\, it should be structur
 ed to include <strong>details of the aims</strong>\, the <strong>econometr
 ic methods used</strong> (in the past some abstracts have not contained ec
 onometric detail so we have been unable to properly assess them)\, and <st
 rong>results</strong>.</p><p>Results should be included even if they are p
 reliminary. Abstracts containing no results or no details of the econometr
 ic methods will be less likely to be accepted.</p><p>Abstracts and papers 
 will be judged primarily on the quality of their econometrics content. We 
 strongly encourage presentation and discussion of work in progress.</p><h3
 >Fees for invited participants</h3><div>Those invited to participate will 
 be asked to pay the registration fee in February 2026.</div><ul><li>Full r
 egistration: AU$600</li><li>PhD students: AU$250</li><li>Low and middle in
 come countries: AU$300*</li></ul><p>*A citizen residing in a country on th
 e <a href="https://datahelpdesk.worldbank.org/knowledgebase/articles/90651
 9-world-bank-country-and-lending-groups">World Bank list</a> of low and mi
 ddle income countries.</p><h4>Inclusions</h4><ul><li>Two nights' accommoda
 tion on Wednesday 15th and Thursday 16th of April</li><li>All meals from l
 unch on Wednesday 15th to lunch on the Friday 17th of April</li></ul><p>Fo
 r additional nights\, you will need to organise them with the hotel direct
 ly.</p><h3>Submissions</h3><p>Electronic submission of papers is required 
 and can be uploaded using the link below. When submitting you will be able
  to choose whether you would like to present a paper\, discuss a paper or 
 chair a session.</p><p><a class="btn" href="https://monash.az1.qualtrics.c
 om/jfe/form/SV_7ODE97lH03z3NDo" target="_blank">Submit your paper</a></p>\
